A local version of '''[[Playhouse Disney]]''' was launched as a [[multiplex]] of Family on November 30, 2007, a commercial-free channel carrying programs aimed at [[preschool]]-aged children, 24 hours a day. Unlike Family, Playhouse Disney has only one national feed operating from the [[North American Eastern Time Zone|Eastern Time Zone]]. For satellite, it is exclusively carried on [[Bell TV]].
